<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TV30">
<l>aṉṉañcel vīrumvaṇ ṭāṉañcel vīrun toḻutirantēṉ</l>
<l>muṉṉañcel vīrkaḷ maṟavēṉmi ṉōkaṇṇaṉ vaikuntaṉō</l>
<l>ṭeṉṉeñci ṉaraikkaṇ ṭāleṉṉaic colli yavariṭainī</l>
<l>riṉṉañcel līrō vituvō takaveṉ ṟicaimiṉkaḷē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>The fruits brought by that Laburnum on the matted hair</l>
<l>come, attached on the side, [and] hang down, it seems, on the blue locks</l>
<l>of the girl of family, at the side of him who has put</l>
<l>that beautiful moon to the left on [his] crown.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
